Class Staff

java.lang.Object
models.User
models.Staff
public class Staff extends User
Represents a Staff member in the system, inheriting from the User class. Stores fields such as the Staff's ID and number of camps managed Contains methods for the Staff to use, such as retrieving Staff ID.
